summary: An Chapel Of Beauty & Love on the outskirts of Windhelm.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#000000][size=3][i]Mine charachter,Anne Scorp is devouted believer of Dibellian faith.
As such she seeks progress in her position in hierarchy of that.

Amongst many deeds of miss.Scorp in the honor of Dibella,the latest is opening of small Shrine to Dibella on the outskirts of Windhelm.

All are welcome to visit this Chapel of Beauty.
If you are seeking meditation,inspiration in musical creativity,
or you just want todrink some wine and enjoy the Sclupture which celebrates the godess of beauty,
you are welcome.

Hope you like it :)[/i][/size][/color][/font]
